-stretch: inherit; font-size: 30px; line-height: 34px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); text-align: start; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Anti_Aging_Dis_Hekimligi_ile_Nasil_Genc_Olunur\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Anti_Aging_Dis_Hekimligi_ile_Nasil_Genc_Olunur\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span><span lang=\"tr\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Anti Aging Diş Hekimliği ile Nasıl Genç Olunur?</span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Dişlerinizin yüz yapınızı destekleme şeklini değiştirmek ve size daha genç görünen bir gülümseme vermek için&nbsp;<a data-ail=\"6575\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://dentnis.com/kozmetik-dis-hekimligi-nedir-tedavileri-nelerdir/\" title=\"kozmetik diş hekimliği\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); background-color: transparent;\">kozmetik diş hekimliği</a>&nbsp;prosedürleri kullanılır. İyi bir&nbsp;<a data-ail=\"6575\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://dentnis.com/gulus-tasarimi/\" title=\"gülüş tasarımı\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); background-color: transparent;\">gülüş tasarımı</a>&nbsp;hem uzun ömürlü sonuçlar verir hem de ameliyatsız bir gençleştirme etkisi yaratır!</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Bazı yaşlanma önleyici diş hekimliği prosedürleri şunları içerebilir:</p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 15px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: outside none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: start; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 14px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc;\">Porselen kaplamalar</li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 14px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc;\">Aynı Gün Lamine Diş</li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 14px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc;\"><a data-mil=\"6575\" href=\"https://dentnis.com/bonding-nedir/\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); background-color: transparent;\">Bonding</a></li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 14px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc;\"><a data-mil=\"6575\" href=\"https://dentnis.com/implant-tedavisi/\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); background-color: transparent;\">Diş implantları</a></li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 14px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc;\"><a data-mil=\"6575\" href=\"https://dentnis.com/dis-beyazlatma/\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); background-color: transparent;\">Diş beyazlatma</a></li></ul><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Tedavi planınız, kişiye özel durumunuza bağlı olarak yukarıdakilerden bir veya daha fazlasını içerebilir.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Yaşlanmayı geciktiren diş hekimliği tedavi seçenekleri ile genellikle kaplama veya kron kombinasyonunu içerir. Bazı hastalarımızda daha iyi dudak desteği ve daha iyi bir gülüş elde etmek için ön dişlerinde dört kaplamaya ihtiyacı olabilir. Bazı hastalarımızda ise tüm gülümseme çizgisinin düzgün bir şekilde görünmesi için on (veya daha fazla) kaplamaya ihtiyaç duyabilir.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing