font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Teknolojik ölçümlerden ve tekniklerden istifade etmek, klinik açıdan bizlere profesyonel anlamda çok başarılı operasyonlar yapmayı sağlarken, hastalarımızın da estetik görünümleri ve konforları bakımından oldukça tatmin edici sonuçlar elde etmelerini sağlar. Bu bağlamda dijital ortamda hazırlanan porselen dolgular, klasik yöntemlerle uygulanan dolgulara nazaran çok daha estetik ve başarılı neticeler ortaya koymaktadır.</p><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; line-height: 34px; font-size: 30px; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); text-align: start; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Neden_Estetik_Porselen_Dolgu\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Neden_Estetik_Porselen_Dolgu\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span>Neden Estetik Porselen Dolgu?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Estetik porselen dolgulara bu ismin verilmesinin nedeni, dolgu içeriğindeki hammaddenin porselen maddesi olmasıdır. Porselen dolgular, hammadde içeriği sayesinde çok daha dayanıklı olmakla birlikte, uzun yıllar sürecek bir koruyuculuk özelliği vardır. Lazer ve kompozit dolgularla mukayese edildiğinde sağladığı avantajlar, tüm dolgu çeşitlerine karşı üstünlük sağlamaktadır.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Ülkemizde en yaygın olarak uygulanan dolgu eski bir yöntem olan amalgam dolgulardır. Uzun yıllar kullanılan bu dolgu çeşidinin en çok tercih edilme sebebi ekonomik açıdan düşük maliyetli oluşudur. Ancak içerdiği cıva maddesi zamanla insan vücudunda toksik etki yaratmaktadır.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Estetik&nbsp; porselen dolgular ise sağlık açısından herhangi bir sağlık tehdidi oluşturmadığı gibi aynı zamanda amalgam dolguların aksine görüntü açısından estetik bir duruş ortaya koyar. Rengi itibariyle&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">gülüş estetiğine</span>&nbsp;olumlu bir katkı sağlayacağı gibi gerektiği durumlarda beyazlatma işlemlerine de tabi tutulabilir; istenilen beyazlık düzeyine ulaştırılabilir. Porselen dolgular boyutlarına göre&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">inlay, onlay</span>&nbsp;ve&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">overlay</span>&nbsp;diye adlandırılır.</p><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; line-height: 34px; font-size: 30px; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); text-align: start; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Estetik_Dolgu_Uygulamasi\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Estetik_Dolgu_Uygulamasi\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span>Estetik Dolgu Uygulaması<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Dişlerde oluşan çürükler nedeni ile bugüne kadar uygulanan birçok farklı yöntem beklenen estetik görüntüyü sağlayamamıştır. Özellikle bir zamanlar herkesin dilinde olan&nbsp;<a data-mil=\"6789\" href=\"https://dentnis.com/amalgam-dolgu/\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 122, 183); background-color: transparent; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px;\">amalgam dolgular</a>, sağlam olsa da siyah görüntüsünden dolayı estetik görünümü bozduğu için yaptıran kişiler&nbsp;<a data-ail=\"6789\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://dentnis.com/dis-beyazlatma/\" title=\"диш беязлатма\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 122, 183); background-color: transparent; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px;\">diş beyazlatma</a>&nbsp;yöntemine ilgi göstermeye başlamıştır.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Amalgam dolguların ortaya çıkardığı kötü görüntü, dişin sağlamlığını unutturmuştur ve görselliğe önem veren kişiler için büyük sorunlar yaratmıştır. Bu nedenle her geçen gün farklı yöntemler ve uygulamalar geliştirilerek insanların sorunlarına en uygun ve en kalıcı çözümler bulunmaya çalışılmaktadır. Bu yöntemlerden biri olan diş beyazlatma yöntemi ile çok kısa sürede bembeyaz dişlere sahip olunabilmektedir. Özellikle dişleri çok sararan ve fırçalasa bile artık sonuç alamayan kişiler bu yöntemden çok memnun kalmaktadır. Diş beyazlatma nedir ve nasıl yapılır aşağıda anlatılmıştır.</p><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; line-height: 34px; font-size: 30px; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); text-align: start; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Estetik_Porselen_Dolgu_Fiyatini_Etkileyen_Faktorler\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Estetik_Porselen_Dolgu_Fiyatini_Etkileyen_Faktorler\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span>Estetik Porselen Dolgu Fiyatını Etkileyen Faktörler<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Эстетический порселен</span><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;должен быть готов к использованию и быть уверенным в том, что все будет в порядке.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">İlk olarak kliniğimizde aldığımız ölçülerin dijital ortama aktarılması ile Laboratuvar ortamında diş ve dişin eksik kısmı 3 boyutlu olarak analiz edilir;&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">ardından Laboratuvarda ölçülere oturacak şekilde dolgu hazırlanır.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Если вы хотите, чтобы вы были уверены в том, что у вас будет возможность получить медицинскую помощь, вам придется пройти долгий путь.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Вы уверены, что это неверная техника, и вы можете избежать неприятных сюрпризов, если это не так.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Эстетика может потребовать длительного лечения, если вы хотите, чтобы этот фактор был действителен, когда речь идет о нестандартных и ненадежных продуктах.&nbsp;</font></font><a data-mil=\"6789\" href=\"https://dentnis.com/dis-dolgusu-fiyatlari/\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 122, 183); background-color: transparent; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Долгу фиятлары</font></a><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;için.</font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Нишанташындаки клинических исследований</span><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;, а также анализ фактов, эдерек ишлем сыраламасы и говорят, что белирлейерек хасталарымыза бир&nbsp;&nbsp;</font><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">эстетик порселен долгу фиятландырмасы</span><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;япмактайиз.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Elbette ki hastalarımız için tedavi maliyeti seçim yapmalarında belirleyici bir faktör olabilmektedir;&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Факат клиники Оларак Биз Сонучлары и Казандырдыги Эстетик Горюнум Ачисиндан Эстетик Порселен Долгую Даха Чок Терцих Этмектейиз Бир Йонтем Оларак.</font></font></p>', 'Обычно существует два разных подхода и метода применения эстетической керамической пломбы. Первая – классическая пломба, вторая – эстетическая фарфоровая пломба. Другими словами, эти пломбы еще называют пломбами.[…]', '2024-02-07 19:15:38', '2024-02-13 05:59:38'),
(18, 3, 2, 'Laminate Veneer', '<h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 30px; line-height: 34px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); text-align: start; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">What Are Laminate Veneers?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Veneers are very thin-formed porcelain surface coatings that can be 0.3 mm thin that are attached to the front part of teeth, beside Zirconia crowns veneers are considered as the best restoration method with a lot of advantages. There are several different types of veneers, each preferable in different patient situations. Typically, the thinner that the Laminate veneer can be made while still remaining strong, the more natural it will appear.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Veneers became the primary choice for those who wished to improve their smiles without removing much of natural teeth.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">The process of the Laminated Veneers consists of at least three stages. In the first stage, the tooth structure of the patient is detaily examinated and the treatment is decided. In the second stage, the measurements are made accordingly to the shape of mouth this process take an average of 1 hour. In the third and final stage, the cut porcelain is adhered to the laminated teeth which the process last approximately 2 hours.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-7405 aligncenter entered lazyloaded\" src=\"https://dentnis.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2023/03/laminate-veneers-before-after-300x180.jpg.webp\" alt=\"Laminate veneers done in Turkey\" width=\"440\" height=\"264\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://dentnis.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2023/03/laminate-veneers-before-after-300x180.jpg.webp 300w,  https://dentnis.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2023/03/laminate-veneers-before-after-1024x614.jpg.webp 1024w,  https://dentnis.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2023/03/laminate-veneers-before-after-768x461.jpg.webp 768w,  https://dentnis.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2023/03/laminate-veneers-before-after-243x146.jpg.webp 243w,  https://dentnis.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2023/03/laminate-veneers-before-after-50x30.jpg.webp 50w,  https://dentnis.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2023/03/laminate-veneers-before-after-125x75.jpg.webp 125w,  https://dentnis.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2023/03/laminate-veneers-before-after.jpg.webp 1200w\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" data-lazy-src=\"https://dentnis.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2023/03/laminate-veneers-before-after-300x180.jpg.webp\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" srcset=\"https://dentnis.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2023/03/laminate-veneers-before-after-300x180.jpg.webp 300w,  https://dentnis.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2023/03/laminate-veneers-before-after-1024x614.jpg.webp 1024w,  https://dentnis.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2023/03/laminate-veneers-before-after-768x461.jpg.webp 768w,  https://dentnis.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2023/03/laminate-veneers-before-after-243x146.jpg.webp 243w,  https://dentnis.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2023/03/laminate-veneers-before-after-50x30.jpg.webp 50w,  https://dentnis.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2023/03/laminate-veneers-before-after-125x75.jpg.webp 125w,  https://dentnis.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2023/03/laminate-veneers-before-after.jpg.webp 1200w\" style=\"height: auto; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; clear: both; text-align: center; display: block;\"></p>', 'Nişantaşı laminate veneers treatment is the process of bonding a porcelain laminate tooth layer onto the existing tooth. Every individual has an aesthetic view that he creates in his own world and determines its qualities.[…]', '2024-02-07 19:17:56', '2024-02-13 06:00:40');
