(20, 4, 2, 'Zirconium outer coating', '<h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 30px; line-height: 34px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Zirconia Crowns</span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Zirconia Crowns are very popular material<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>known for superior toughness, strength, and fatigue resistance, in addition to excellent wear properties and biocompatibility making it an ideal option for dental crowns. Not only are they incredibly strong and long-lasting, but they are made to mimic the look and feel of real teeth when placed in the mouth and help to even out and fill in your smile.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Oftentimes, crowns are needed when a tooth has become compromised or damaged.</p><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 30px; line-height: 34px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); text-align: start; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Zirconia_Crowns_Application\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Zirconia_Crowns_Application\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span>Zirconia Crowns Application<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">The first step is to evaluate the necessity of zirconium coating treatment, afterwards if zirconium coating treatment is appropriate for our patient local anesthesia is used on the area of the treatment. Impressions are taken in order to be used to create your new zirconia crown. Your next appointment involves actually placing the permanent zirconia crown and filing it down. Your new crown can last for many years and provide you with a bright and full&nbsp;<a data-mil=\"7484\" href=\"https://dentnis.com/en/smile-design/\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); background-color: transparent;\">smile design</a>.</p><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 30px; line-height: 34px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); text-align: start; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Advantages_of_Zirconia_Crowns\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Advantages_of_Zirconia_Crowns\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span>Advantages of Zirconia Crowns<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Zirconia crowns are made of strong, durable material ,it can be easily modified, reshaped, and recolored, they are highly biocompatible not containing<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>metal which prevents darkening around the gingival area, and are suitable for patients with metal allergies too.</p>', 'Zirconium dental coating treatments are frequently used in tissue loss and root canal treatments due to tooth decay or trauma over time. Realized with various techniques and materials […]', '2024-02-07 19:20:10', '2024-02-14 03:32:24');
