t; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Zirkonyum_Dis_Omru\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Zirkonyum_Dis_Omru\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Zirkonyum Diş Ömrü</span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Diş kaplamalarının ömrünü etkileyen en önemli faktörlerden biri düzenli ve doğru ağız hijyenidir. Dişlerinizi düzenli olarak fırçalamak, diş ipi kullanmak ve diş hekiminizin tavsiyelerine uygun şekilde temizlik yapmak zirkonyum kaplamaların dayanıklılığını artırabilir. Bu şartlara uygun bir zirkonyum dişin ömrü 20 yıla kadar sürebilir.&nbsp;<a data-mil=\"7481\" href=\"https://dentnis.com/dr-abdulkadir-narin/\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 122, 183); background-color: transparent; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px;\">Doktor Abdulkadir Narin’i</a>&nbsp;tercih ederek daha sağlıklı ve gülüşünüz için en uygun zirkonyum diş kaplamasını yaptırabilirsiniz.</p><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; line-height: 34px; font-size: 30px; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); text-align: start; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Zirkonyum_Dis_Kaplama_Ne_Kadar_Zaman_Alir\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Zirkonyum_Dis_Kaplama_Ne_Kadar_Zaman_Alir\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Zirkonyum Diş Kaplama Ne Kadar Zaman Alır?</span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Dişteki problemlerin tespiti ve giderilme süreci sonrasında dişler şekillendirilme işlemine tabi tutulur. Sonrasında alınan ölçülere göre zirkonyum kaplama dişlerin yapım aşaması başlar. Bu işlem 1 hafta kadar sürer. Bir haftanın sonunda hazır olan dişler 10-15 dakika gibi bir sürede dişlere yapıştırılır. Tedavi sonrasında hastalarımız aynı gün içerisinde günlük hayatlarına geri dönebilirler.</p><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; line-height: 34px; font-size: 30px; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); text-align: left; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Zirkonyum_Dis_Teknolojisi_Nedir\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Zirkonyum_Dis_Teknolojisi_Nedir\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Zirkonyum Diş Teknolojisi Nedir?</span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Zirkonyum diş kaplama tedavisi iki yönde gelişim göstermektedir: bu gelişimlerden biri ölçü alma tekniklerindeki gelişimlerdir; diğeri ise kaplamanın üretim aşamasında meydana gelen gelişimlerdir. Her iki süreçte de artık yoğun olarak dijital imkânlardan faydalanılmaktadır.&nbsp;<a data-mil=\"7481\" href=\"https://dentnis.com/dijital-dis-hekimligi/\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 122, 183); background-color: transparent; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px;\">Bilgisayar destekli taramalarla</a>&nbsp;elde edilen ölçülerdeki diş görüntüsü sayesinde tıpkı bireylerin parmak izlerinin yalnızca kendilerine ait olması gibi dijital araçlarla üretilen dişler de ölçümlerle birebir uyumlu olmaktadır. Bu aşamaların dijital destekli olması, manuel uygulamalardaki hata riskini ortadan kaldırır hem de tedavi süreçlerinin daha kısa sürede nihayetlendirilmesini sağlar. Bu bakımdan dijital destekli tedaviler kusursuz sonuçlar meydana getirmektedir.</p><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; line-height: 34px; font-size: 30px; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); text-align: left; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tek_Bir_Dise_Yapilabilir_mi\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Tek_Bir_Dise_Yapilabilir_mi\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Tek Bir Dişe Yapılabilir mi?</span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Yüzeyinde çürük ya da kırık oluşmuş bir tek dişin varlığında diğer dişlerle estetik ve yapı itibariyle bütünlük sağlanacak şekilde zirkonyum kaplama tedavisi uygulamak mümkündür. Bu uygulama sayesinde estetik fark oluşmaksızın tek dişe kaplama uygulaması yapabilmekteyiz.</p><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; line-height: 34px; font-size: 30px; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); text-align: left; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Disimizde_Kirik_veya_Curuk_Varsa_Yapilabilir_mi\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Disimizde_Kirik_veya_Curuk_Varsa_Yapilabilir_mi\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Dişimizde Kırık veya Çürük Varsa Yapılabilir mi?</span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Tedavi uygulanacak bölgedeki mevcut çürük ya da kırığın ne ölçüde derinlik kazandığı bu tekniğin uygulanması noktasında belirleyici faktördür. Bazı durumlarda farklı alternatif çözüm yollarını tercih edebilmekteyiz. Fakat dişi zayıflatacak bir doku kaybına neden olan çürük ya da kırık mevcudiyeti söz konusu ise zirkonyum diş kaplama tedavisi elzem hale gelmiş demektir.</p><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; line-height: 34px; font-size: 30px; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); text-align: start; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Zirkonyum_Dis_Kaplama_Fiyatlari\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Zirkonyum_Dis_Kaplama_Fiyatlari\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Zirkonyum Diş Kaplama Fiyatları</span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\"><a data-mil=\"7481\" href=\"https://dentnis.com/zirkonyum-kaplama-fiyatlari/\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 122, 183); background-color: transparent; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px;\">Zirkonyum Kaplama Fiyatları 2023</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.doktortakvimi.com/abdulkadir-narin/dis-hekimi/istanbul\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 122, 183); background-color: transparent; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px;\">Dt. Abdulkadir Narin</a><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;Он варьируется, потому что он разработан специально для каждого человека.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Объем проводимого лечения варьируется от человека к человеку и в зависимости от используемой лаборатории.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Это один из самых эстетичных типов зубных виниров, которые мы рекомендуем нашим пациентам, он изготовлен из высококачественного и естественно выглядящего циркониевого материала.</font></font></p><p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\"><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/doktornarin/\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 122, 183); background-color: transparent; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Инстаграм</span></a><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">&nbsp;На нашем сайте вы можете посмотреть фотографии до и после лечения.</span></p><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; line-height: 34px; font-size: 30px; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); text-align: left; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Zirkonyum_Dis_Dogal_Gorunur_mu\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Zirkonyum_Dis_Dogal_Gorunur_mu\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Выглядят ли циркониевые зубы естественными?</span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Благодаря входящему в состав материалу очень успешно достигается естественный внешний вид зубов.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Он имеет внешний вид, неотличимый от натуральных зубов, особенно благодаря светопроницаемости и прозрачности по отношению к кончикам зубов.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Кроме того, поскольку это не метод покрытия на металлической основе, не возникает эстетических проблем, таких как поседение со временем и темное отражение цвета на деснах.</font></font></p><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; line-height: 34px; font-size: 30px; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); text-align: start; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Zirkonyum_Dis_Kaplama_Metal_Destekli_Porselen_Kaplamadan_Neden_Daha_Pahalidir\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Zirkonyum_Dis_Kaplama_Metal_Destekli_Porselen_Kaplamadan_Neden_Daha_Pahalidir\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Почему циркониевые зубные виниры дороже фарфоровых виниров на металлической основе?</span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Основная причина, по которой это дороже, связана с необходимостью трудоемкой работы.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Циркониевый материал производится дороже, поскольку он требует более высокой технологической инфраструктуры, и в то же время рабочая сила, которая может подготовить этот материал для получения желаемого эстетического результата и желаемых адаптационных функций, является более дорогостоящим фактором.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Короче говоря, мы можем сказать, что это связано с разницей в стоимости между старой и новой технологией.</font></font></p><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; line-height: 34px; font-size: 30px; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); text-align: start; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Lamina_ve_Zirkonyum_Arasindaki_Farklar_Nelerdir\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Lamina_ve_Zirkonyum_Arasindaki_Farklar_Nelerdir\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">В чем разница между пластинкой и цирконием?</span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Между этими двумя методами нанесения покрытия есть много различий, но наиболее очевидным является;&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Прежде чем на зуб можно будет нанести циркониевое покрытие, на зубах необходимо сделать надрез.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Если в зубе есть состояния, требующие восстановления, нанесение циркониевого покрытия на эту область будет более здоровым и подходящим подходом.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Однако при использовании ламинированных зубных виниров никаких действий в отношении размера зубов не предпринимается.</font></font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Если вам интересно&nbsp;</font><a data-mil=\"7481\" href=\"https://dentnis.com/zirkonyum-dis-mi-porselen-dis-mi/\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 122, 183); background-color: transparent; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">циркониевые зубы или фарфоровые зубы?</font></a><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;Вы также можете посмотреть нашу статью.</font></p><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; line-height: 34px; font-size: 30px; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); text-align: start; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Zirkonyum_Yerine_Lamina_Neden_Tercih_Edilmemektedir\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Zirkonyum_Yerine_Lamina_Neden_Tercih_Edilmemektedir\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Почему пластинка не предпочтительнее циркония?</span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">При потере тканей в случаях кариеса или поломки циркониевого покрытия зуба;&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Если имеется нарушение зубного ряда;&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">до зуба&nbsp;</font></font><a data-ail=\"7481\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://dentnis.com/kanal-tedavisi/\" title=\"лечение корневых каналов\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 122, 183); background-color: transparent; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">лечение корневых каналов</font></a><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;Если это будет реализовано, это станет необходимостью.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Все эти проблемы требуют циркониевого покрытия, поскольку это проблемы со здоровьем, которые необходимо устранить.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Однако ламинатные покрытия наносятся исключительно в эстетических целях.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Другими словами, если в зубе есть нездоровая ткань, это приведет к прорезыванию зуба;&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Однако покрытие ламинатом не является методом обработки, применяемым в этом направлении.</font></font></p>', 'Обработка зубных покрытий цирконием часто используется при потере тканей и лечении корневых каналов из-за кариеса или травмы с течением времени. Выполнено с использованием различных техник и материалов […]', '