3/dis-eti-tedavisi-image-1.jpg\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" sizes=\"(max-width: 452px) 100vw, 452px\" srcset=\"https://dentnis.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2020/03/dis-eti-tedavisi-image-1.jpg.webp 500w,  https://dentnis.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2020/03/dis-eti-tedavisi-image-1-300x200.jpg.webp 300w\" style=\"height: auto; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px rgb(226, 226, 226); font: inherit; display: inline;\"><p id=\"caption-attachment-512\" class=\"wp-caption-text\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 5px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(166, 166, 166); text-align: center; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">Gingival Recession (Periodontology)</p></div><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Once the cause of the gingival recession has been addressed the procedure starts by<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>applying<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>root surface cleaning, interface cleaning,<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>bleaching processes (<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><a data-mil=\"6746\" href=\"https://dentnis.com/en/teeth-whitening/\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); background-color: transparent;\">teeth&nbsp;whitening</a>)&nbsp;</span>and offer our patients suggestions for the care they need to do to ensure oral hygiene.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Every case of gum recession is slightly different, therefore many treatments are available.</p><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 30px; line-height: 34px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); text-align: start; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Surgical_Treatments\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Surgical_Treatments\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span>Surgical Treatments<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">We aim to complete the improvements we have achieved in the initial treatment we apply in our clinic after several<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>sessions and move on to the other necessary stages.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">By determining the general oral condition and gingival phenotype of our patients, we decide on other treatment stages and our Doctor performs several surgical techniques to correct receding gums and increase the amount of attached tissue.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">These operations can be listed as follows;</p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 15px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: outside none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: start; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 14px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc;\">Regenerative treatments and graft applications.</li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 14px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc;\">Gingival levels and gingival aesthetic.</li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 14px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; 