box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px !important; text-align: start; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Kliniğimizde uyguladığımız başlangıç tedavisini 2 ila 3 seans neticesinde tamamlayıp, gerekli olan diğer aşamalara geçmeyi hedeflemekteyiz. Hastalarımızın genel ağız sağlığı durumunu ve diş eti fenotipini belirleyerek diğer tedavi aşamalarını kararlaştırır ve bu doğrultuda birtakım cerrahi operasyonlar uygularız. Bu operasyonlar aşağıdaki gibi sıralanabilir;</p><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 15px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: outside none;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 14px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc;\">Rejeneratif tedaviler ve gretf uygulamaları</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 14px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc;\">Diş eti seviyelemeleri ve pembe estetik</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 14px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc;\">Kuron boyu uzatma</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 14px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc;\">Diş eti cep eliminasyonu operasyonları</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 14px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc;\">Dental implantlar</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 14px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc;\">Lazer uygulamaları</li></ul><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px 10px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; font-size: 24px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Dis_Eti_Cekilmesi_Restoratif_Tedaviler\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Dis_Eti_Cekilmesi_Restoratif_Tedaviler\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span>Diş Eti Çekilmesi Restoratif Tedaviler<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px !important; text-align: start; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Bu aşamada, mikrobiyal plak birikiminin gözlendiği eski veya taşkın olan dolgu ve kaplamaların yenilenmesi, eksik dişlerin telafisi ve fonksiyonel dengenin sağlanması ile diş eti hastalığına zemin hazırlayan faktörlerin giderilmesi sağlanır.</p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px 10px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 34px; font-size: 30px; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); text-align: center; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: 0px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Idame_Tedavilerinin_Onemi\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Idame_Tedavilerinin_Onemi\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span>İdame Tedavilerinin Önemi<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px !important; text-align: start; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Cerrahi ve restoratif tedavilerle elde edilen iyileşmenin muhafazasının sağlanması için klinik muayene ve kontrollerin aksatılmaması son derece hayati bir önem arz etmektedir. Bu açıdan kliniğimizde hastalarımıza uyguladığımız tedavilerle aynı hassasiyette sürdürdüğümüz takip sistemimiz sayesinde siz hastalarımızla periodontal ve genel ağız diş sağlığınızın idamesi için gerekli tedavi ve kontrol süreçlerini belirlemekte; gereksinim duyduğunuz motivasyonu profesyonel bir yaklaşımla sizlere sunmaktayız.</p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px 10px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 34px; font-size: 30px; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); text-align: center; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: 0px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Dis_Eti_Sagligi\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Dis_Eti_Sagligi\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span>Diş Eti Sağlığı<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px !important; text-align: start; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Ağız sağlığı, bireylerin yaşama dâhil olmalarındaki tüm faaliyetlerine ciddi anlamda etkide bulunmaktadır; çünkü insanın temel ihtiyacı olan beslenme için sindirim ağızda başlar. Bu nedenle kaliteli beslenebilmek için sağlıklı bir ağız yapısına sahip olmak da büyük önem teşkil etmektedir.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px !important; text-align: start; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Sağlıklı bir ağız ve sağlıklı bir estetik&nbsp;<a data-mil=\"6744\" href=\"https://dentnis.com/gulus-tasarimi/\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); text-decoration: none; background: transparent; display: inline-block; text-align: center; padding: 0px; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px;\">gülüş tasarımı</a>&nbsp;için elzem olan anahtar kavramlardan biri de diş eti sağlığıdır. Diş eti sağlığının kaybedildiği durumlarda ise&nbsp;<a data-mil=\"6744\" href=\"https://dentnis.com/pembe-estetik/\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); text-decoration: none; background: transparent; display: inline-block; text-align: center; padding: 0px; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px;\">pembe estetik</a>&nbsp;dâhilinde uygulanan operasyonlardan istifade edilmesi, ağız sağlığı ve estetik neticeleri arasındaki döngüyü yeniden sağlıklı bir şekilde işler hale getirecektir.</p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px 10px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; font-size: 24px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Koruyucu_ve_Onleyici_Uygulamalar\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Koruyucu_ve_Onleyici_Uygulamalar\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span>Koruyucu ve Önleyici Uygulamalar<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px !important; text-align: start; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Ağız içinde sayısız bakteri ve canlı mikroorganizmalar mevcuttur. Bu bakteri ve mikroorganizmalar diş yüzeyinde diş taşı olarak adlandırılan plaklar üzerinde adeta koloni kurar ve hem dişin hem de diş etinin sağlığını tehdit eder.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px !important; text-align: start; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\">Со временем происходит потеря десен;<span>&nbsp;</span></font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\">Эта ситуация также создает риск потери зубов.<span>&nbsp;</span></font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\">Поэтому, прежде всего, следует приложить усилия для предотвращения образования этих бляшек с помощью защитных и профилактических мероприятий;<span>&nbsp;</span></font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\">Если его образование невозможно предотвратить, его необходимо устранить с помощью таких методов, как чистка и механическое отбеливание.</font></font></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px !important; text-align: start; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\">В противном случае возможно возникновение воспаления, называемого «гингивит», которое проявляется в виде простой кровоточивости десен.</font></font></p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px 10px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 34px; font-size: 30px; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); text-align: center; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: 0px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Gingivitis_Problemi\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Gingivitis_Problemi\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\">Проблема гингивита</font></font><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px !important; text-align: start; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\">Проблема гингивита решается регулярным посещением стоматолога и ежегодным лечением.&nbsp;</font></font><a data-mil=\"6744\" href=\"https://dentnis.com/dis-tasi-temizligi-nedir/\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); text-decoration: none; background: transparent; display: inline-block; text-align: center; padding: 0px; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\">чистка зубного камня</font></font></a><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;и может быть устранено без хирургического вмешательства.</font></font></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px !important; text-align: start; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\">Это не приводит к потере костей или зубов.<span>&nbsp;</span></font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\">Однако если оно прогрессирует, нездоровое состояние десен углубляется;<span>&nbsp;</span></font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\">Со временем может произойти рецессия десен и потеря тканей и челюстной кости.<span>&nbsp;</span></font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\">Такая ситуация повлечет за собой последствия вплоть до потери зуба.</font></font></p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px 10px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 34px; font-size: 30px; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); text-align: center; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: 0px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Dis_Eti_Cekilmesi_Kanamasi\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Dis_Eti_Cekilmesi_Kanamasi\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\">Кровотечение при рецессии десен</font></font><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px !important; text-align: start; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\">Мы наблюдаем множество клинических симптомов заболеваний десен.<span>&nbsp;</span></font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\">Эти;<span>&nbsp;</span></font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\">Такие проблемы, как покраснение десен, кровотечение, неприятный запах изо рта, боль при жевании и рецессия десен.<span>&nbsp;</span></font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\">Различия в общем состоянии здоровья наших пациентов также могут стать причиной их предрасположенности к заболеваниям десен.<span>&nbsp;</span></font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\">Некоторые препараты используются особенно в связи с гормональным балансом подростков и женщин, беременностью женщин, курением, диабетом и системными заболеваниями;<span>&nbsp;</span></font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\">Это может увеличить восприимчивость к заболеваниям десен.</font></font></p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px 10px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 34px; font-size: 30px; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); text-align: center; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: 0px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Dis_Eti_Cekilmesi_Tedavi_Cozumleri\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Dis_Eti_Cekilmesi_Tedavi_Cozumleri\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\">Решения для лечения рецессии десен</font></font><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px !important; text-align: start; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\">Заболевания десен не являются локальными проблемами, ограничивающимися по зоне воздействия внутренней частью рта;<span>&nbsp;</span></font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\">Области его влияния довольно широки, поскольку он прямо или косвенно влияет на иммунную систему человека.<span>&nbsp;</span></font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\">В результате люди могут стать более склонными к заболеваниям.</font></font></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px !important; text-align: start; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\">Люди с заболеваниями десен подвергаются большему риску возникновения нарушений пищеварения и системы кровообращения, чем здоровые люди.<span>&nbsp;</span></font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\">Это сопряжено с риском сердечно-сосудистых заболеваний, и было замечено, что у этих пациентов труднее контролировать уровень сахара в крови.<span>&nbsp;</span></font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\">Поэтому стоматологическая помощь и осмотры имеют жизненно важное значение.<span>&nbsp;</span></font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\">Не следует пренебрегать уходом за полостью рта и избегать практики, которая может поставить под угрозу здоровье полости рта.<span>&nbsp;</span></font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\">Регулярная и правильная чистка зубов должна стать привычкой, чтобы предотвратить многие проблемы со здоровьем.</font></font></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px !important; text-align: start; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\">Вам обязательно следует посещать стоматолога один раз в год для устранения зубного камня и использования методов профилактического лечения.<span>&nbsp;</span></font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\">Защита здоровья до возникновения заболевания и применение профилактического лечения являются жизненно важными и приоритетными подходами к защите здоровья зубов.<span>&nbsp;</span></font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\">Благодаря чистке зубного камня зубы становятся белее;<span>&nbsp;</span></font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\">В то же время десны защищаются от воспаления и укрепляется здоровье десен.</font></font></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px !important; text-align: start; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\">В Турции уже растет привычка чистить зубы.<span>&nbsp;</span></font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\">Однако из-за особенностей питания, различий в структуре слюны и недостаточной эффективности чистки зубов они все равно обращаются к стоматологу, заботятся о здоровье десен и&nbsp;</font></font><a data-mil=\"6744\" href=\"https://dentnis.com/dis-estetigi-ile-genclesmek-mumkun/\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); text-decoration: none; background: transparent; display: inline-block; text-align: center; padding: 0px; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\">эстетика зубов</font></font></a><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;Существует большая польза с точки зрения<span>&nbsp;</span></font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;\">Поэтому чистку следует проводить раз в год, чтобы повысить мотивацию чистки зубов, устранить желтизну и сохранить здоровье десен.</font></font></p></div></div></div></div></div>', 'Рецессия десен повлияет не только на вашу жевательную функцию; Ваша улыбка будет испорчена и из-за потери эстетического вида десен из-за их рецессии. Потому что в нездоровой десне; рецессия десен […]', '2024-02-07 19:26:34', '2024-02-14 03:34:53');
INSERT INTO `blog_translations` (`id`, `blog_id`, `language_id`, `title`, `description`, `mini_description`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(26, 9, 2, 'pediatric dentistry', '<h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 30px; line-height: 34px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); text-align: start; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">Pedodontics<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Pediatric dentistry</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">(pedodontics)</span>&nbsp;is the general name of treatment methods for dental and oral health suitable for all stages of childhood. All methods preferred in&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">pedodontics</span>&nbsp;are preferred by adhering to physiological and psychological developments that vary depending on the age ranges of children. These treatment methods cover the period from the time when the deciduous teeth started to have erupted until the adolescence.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">The primary goal of pedodontics is to ensure that the deciduous teeth that last before permanent teeth are kept in a healthy mouth. If deciduous teeth are unhealthy or lost, it is important to take precautions in order not to risk the health of permanent teeth. In other words, pedodontics aims to maintain the health of deciduous teeth and to keep permanent teeth healthy in the mouth.</p><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 30px; line-height: 34px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); text-align: start; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_Importance_of_Deciduous_Teeth\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#The_Importance_of_Deciduous_Teeth\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span>The Importance of Deciduous Teeth<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><div id=\"attachment_514\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 8px solid rgb(248, 248, 248); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 0; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); width: 423px;\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-514\" class=\"wp-image-514 entered lazyloaded\" src=\"https://dentnis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/cocuk-dis-hekimligi-image-1.jpg\" alt=\"Pediatric Dentistry\" width=\"413\" height=\"275\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://dentnis.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2020/03/cocuk-dis-hekimligi-image-1.jpg.webp 500w,  https://dentnis.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2020/03/cocuk-dis-hekimligi-image-1-300x200.jpg.webp 300w\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 413px) 100vw, 413px\" data-lazy-src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/cocuk-dis-hekimligi-image-1.jpg\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" sizes=\"(max-width: 413px) 100vw, 413px\" srcset=\"https://dentnis.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2020/03/cocuk-dis-hekimligi-image-1.jpg.webp 500w,  https://dentnis.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2020/03/cocuk-dis-hekimligi-image-1-300x200.jpg.webp 300w\" style=\"height: auto; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px rgb(226, 226, 226); font: inherit; display: inline;\"><p id=\"caption-attachment-514\" class=\"wp-caption-text\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 5px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(166, 166, 166); text-align: center; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">Pediatric Dentistry</p></div><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Deciduous teeth, which begin to erupt within the first six months of infancy, accompany individuals in childhood until permanent teeth erupted take their place in the mouth. In this regard, deciduous teeth can be permanent, even if they are not permanent, either because of the duty they undertake during the development period and because they shape the existence and alignment of permanent teeth that will be erupted.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">On the general acceptance, deciduous teeth erupt in the 5 to 6 months and the stay until the permanent teeth take their place in the mouth between 24 and 30 months. There are many skills gained during childhood; such as chewing and speaking.</p><h3 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: start; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Pediatric_Dentistry\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Pediatric_Dentistry\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span>Pediatric Dentistry<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Pediatric Dentistry ;For all these functions to develop completely, a healthy mouth and teeth structure is required. The problems experienced in terms of oral health will also hinder the development and functioning of these capabilities. Physiological disorders that occur during childhood may cause psychological traumas in children who are about to be adults.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Especially the problems experienced in terms of oral health and aesthetics have a determinative impact in terms of the aesthetic integrity of the face, which may be the reason psychological problems such as lack of self-confidence, shyness and anxiety children.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">If deciduous teeth are broken, decayed, or lost for some reason, nutritional problems will arise; Developmental problems may be seen in cases where nutrition is inadequate which have a crucial effect on physiological development. Because malnutrition leads to an improper development process.</p><h4 style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: start; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Pediatric_Dentistry-2\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Pediatric_Dentistry-2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span>Pediatric Dentistry<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h4><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">One of the most important duties of deciduous teeth is guiding permanent teeth. Here, there is a social misunderstanding about the issue: the statement that ‘Deciduous teeth are not permanent and not cared about too much’ is a mistake and causes huge problems related to oral health,.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">However, deciduous teeth maintain the eruption of the permanent teeth and act as a guide for them to be kept in the mouth. By keeping the deciduous teeth in a healthy mouth, permanent teeth are positioned properly and the desired tooth alignment is provided.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">However, if the deciduous teeth are lost earlier than expected, the other teeth slide towards the gap created by the missing tooth and as a result, the tooth alignment is impaired. The permanent teeth coming from after deciduous teeth cannot be positioned properly under these conditions and the general alignment of the teeth is lost.</p><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 30px; line-height: 34px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); text-align: start; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_Problem_of_Early_Loss_of_Deciduous_Teeth\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#The_Problem_of_Early_Loss_of_Deciduous_Teeth\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span>The Problem of Early Loss of Deciduous Teeth<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">In a research carried out at Ankara University, it was determined that 87% of five thousand patients who received orthodontic braces treatment had orthodontic problems due to early loss of deciduous teeth.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">As a result of this research, it clearly shows us the importance of deciduous teeth and proves that what extent permanent teeth are affected by the fate of the deciduous teeth. In a way, we can say that deciduous teeth are an important factor in determining the fate of permanent teeth.</p><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 30px; line-height: 34px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); text-align: start; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Treatment_Methods_for_Deciduous_Teeth\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Treatment_Methods_for_Deciduous_Teeth\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span>Treatment Methods for Deciduous Teeth<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Overall our clinical approach is primarily to explain the importance of deciduous teeth to parents and encourage them to take the necessary care to protect the existence of deciduous teeth. However, in case of decay in deciduous teeth or loss for any reason, it becomes essential to fill the cavity with a method called “placeholder” to prevent the alignment abnormality of the other teeth. In this way, the position of the other teeth and the future permanent teeth are maintained.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Otherwise, braces may be required in the majority of children who have been exposed to such problems in the future. Another application is the so-called “fissure sealant” for preventing the formation of caries and plaque on the tooth surfaces.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Thanks to this method, both the deciduous teeth are protected and caries that may occur during the application of the permanent teeth are prevented.</p><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 30px; line-height: 34px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); text-align: start; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Dental_Care_in_Children\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Dental_Care_in_Children\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span>Dental Care in Children<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Children cannot provide efficient dental care in terms of both cognitive and hand ability. For this reason, it will be a necessary and healthy approach for parents to undertake dental care of their children, especially in the period up to 5 years old. It is useful to clean the mouth, as food residues will accumulate in the mouth during the transition period from breast milk to solid foods, especially during infancy.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">In addition to helping children, the best thing to do is to teach them proper dental care and oral hygiene. Children with this care will be more elaborate individuals regarding dental care as well as individuals without bias in terms of dental treatments and dentist examination.</p><h3 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: start; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Dental_Care\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Dental_Care\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span>Dental Care<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">It will be useful to introduce children with the dentist at the age of 1 to enlighten and educate them about improper applications. In particular, parents should be warned against baby bottle decays. Another proper approach that supports this dental care is to introduce children with a dentist at the age of 3-4 years.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">It is also important to bring children to routine dental visits at the age of 3-4 for preventive measures. In this process, parents are advised to brush their children’s teeth with automatic toothbrushes. Toothpaste produced for children is also important for dental care.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">While the parents are guided by the dentist with the proper practices, the children will grow without prejudgment against any future dental treatment and have no fear of dentist. Again, the fissure sealant treatment will act as a shield against dental decays that may occur in childhood</p>', 'Pediatric Dentistry (Pedodontics) Pediatric dentistry (pedodontics) is the general name of treatment methods for dental and oral health suitable for every stage of child development. Within pediatric dentistry […]', '2024-02-07 19:28:41', '2024-02-14 03:35:56');
