(27, 9, 3, 'детская стоматология', '<div class=\"vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid\" style=\"margin: 0px -15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; width: 946.662px; position: relative; min-height: 1px; float: left;\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 15px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; width: 946.662px;\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><div class=\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 35px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; line-height: 34px; font-size: 30px; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: 0px;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Детская стоматология (педодонтия)</font><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 20px !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Детская стоматология</span><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;(педодонтия) — общее название методов лечения зубов и полости рта, подходящих для любого этапа развития ребенка.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;Все методы, предпочтительные в&nbsp;</font></font><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">детской стоматологии, отдаются предпочтением с учетом физиологических и психологических особенностей развития, которые варьируются в зависимости от возрастного диапазона детей.&nbsp;</span><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Эти методы лечения охватывают период от периода первого прорезывания молочных зубов до подросткового возраста.</font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 20px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Основная цель методов детской стоматологии – обеспечить здоровое сохранение во рту молочных зубов, прорезывающихся раньше постоянных.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">В случае, если молочные зубы нездоровы или потеряны, необходимо принять меры предосторожности, чтобы не поставить под угрозу здоровье постоянных зубов.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Другими словами, методы детской стоматологии направлены на сохранение здоровья молочных зубов и обеспечение здорового прорезывания постоянных зубов во рту.</font></font></p><div id=\"attachment_514\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 35px; padding: 0px; border: 8px solid rgb(248, 248, 248); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 0; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; max-width: 100%; width: 480px;\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-514\" class=\"wp-image-514 entered lazyloaded\" src=\"https://dentnis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/cocuk-dis-hekimligi-image-1.jpg\" alt=\"Детская стоматология\" width=\"470\" height=\"313\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://dentnis.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2020/03/cocuk-dis-hekimligi-image-1.jpg.webp 500w,  https://dentnis.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2020/03/cocuk-dis-hekimligi-image-1-300x200.jpg.webp 300w\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 470px) 100vw, 470px\" data-lazy-src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/cocuk-dis-hekimligi-image-1.jpg\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" sizes=\"(max-width: 470px) 100vw, 470px\" srcset=\"https://dentnis.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2020/03/cocuk-dis-hekimligi-image-1.jpg.webp 500w,  https://dentnis.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2020/03/cocuk-dis-hekimligi-image-1-300x200.jpg.webp 300w\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(226, 226, 226); height: auto; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font: inherit; display: inline;\"><p id=\"caption-attachment-514\" class=\"wp-caption-text\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; text-align: center; padding: 10px 0px 5px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(166, 166, 166); background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Детская стоматология</font></p></div><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; line-height: 34px; font-size: 30px; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: 0px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Sut_Dislerinin_Onemi\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Sut_Dislerinin_Onemi\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Важность молочных зубов</font><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 20px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Молочные зубы, которые обычно начинают прорезываться в первые шесть месяцев младенчества, сопровождают человека на протяжении всего детства, пока его место во рту не займут постоянные зубы.</font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 20px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">В этом отношении, хотя молочные зубы сами по себе не являются постоянными, они могут быть постоянными по своим последствиям, поскольку определяют как период развития, так и существование постоянных зубов.</font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 20px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">По общепринятому мнению, молочные зубы впервые прорезываются во рту младенцев в возрасте от 5 до 6 месяцев, а последние занимают свое место во рту между 24 и 30 месяцами.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">В период развития приобретается множество навыков;&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Это такие функции, как жевание и речь.</font></font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 20px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Здоровая структура рта и зубов необходима для полноценного развития всех этих функций.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Негативные явления в отношении общего состояния полости рта также нарушают развитие и функционирование этих способностей.</font></font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 20px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Физиологические нарушения, возникающие в процессе развития, могут стать причиной психологической травмы у детей, находящихся на пути становления личности.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Особенно проблемы со здоровьем полости рта и эстетикой, которые имеют решающее значение с точки зрения эстетической целостности лица.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Это может вызвать у детей нездоровое настроение, такое как неуверенность в себе, интроверсия и хроническое беспокойство.</font></font></p><h3 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.1; font-size: 24px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Sut_Disleri_Neden_Onemlidir\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Sut_Disleri_Neden_Onemlidir\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Почему важны молочные зубы?</span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Süt dişlerinin kırılması, çürümesi veya bir sebeple kaybedilmesi halinde beslenme sorunları ortaya çıkacaktır; beslenmenin ise çocuk gelişimi üzerinde belirleyici rol üstlenmesi bakımından yetersiz olduğu durumlarda gelişim problemleri meydana gelecektir. Çünkü sağlıksız beslenme, sağlıksız gelişim sürecini doğurur. Süt dişlerinin en önemli vazifelerinden biri ise arkasından gelecek olan daimi dişler için rehberlik yapmasıdır.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">İşte, tam bu hususta toplumsal bir yanılgı söz konusu olmaktadır. Süt dişlerinin daimi olmaması nedeniyle çok fazla önemsenmemesi ağız sağlığı yönünden olumsuz neticeler doğuran bir yanılgıdır. Hâlbuki süt dişleri daimi dişlerin germini muhafaza ederek onların sağlıklı bir şekilde vakti geldiğinde ağızda sürmesinde yol göstericilik vazifesini üstlenir.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Süt dişlerinin sağlıklı bir şekilde ağızda tutulması sayesinde daimi dişler de doğru bir şekilde konumlanır ve estetik bir diş dizilimi sağlanır. Ama süt dişlerinin erken kaybedilmesi durumunda diğer dişler eksilen dişin meydana getirdiği boşluğa doğru kayar ve sonuç olarak diş dizilimi bozulur. Arkadan gelecek olan daimi dişler de bu şartlarda doğru bir şekilde konumlanamaz ve dişlerin genel estetik dizilimi kaybedilir.</p><h3 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.1; font-size: 24px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Sut_Dislerin_Erken_Kaybi_Sorunu\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Sut_Dislerin_Erken_Kaybi_Sorunu\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Süt Dişlerin Erken Kaybı Sorunu</span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Ankara Üniversitesi’nde yapılan araştırmada ortodontik&nbsp;<a data-ail=\"6620\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://dentnis.com/dis-teli-tedavisi/\" title=\"лечение брекетами\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 122, 183); background-color: transparent; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px;\">diş teli tedavisi</a>&nbsp;gören beş bin hastanın %87’sinin süt dişini erken kaybetmiştir. Bu nedeniyle ortodontik problemler yaşadığı ve bu nedenle ortodontik diş teli tedavisi gördüğü tespit edilmiştir.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Bu araştırma sonucu bizlere süt dişlerin önemini apaçık bir şekilde göstermekte ve daimi dişlerin kaderini ne ölçüde etkilediğini ispat etmektedir. Bir bakıma diyebiliriz ki süt dişler, daimi dişlerin kaderini belirlemede etken bir faktördür.</p><h3 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.1; font-size: 24px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Sut_Dislerine_Yonelik_Tedavi_Yontemleri\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Sut_Dislerine_Yonelik_Tedavi_Yontemleri\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Süt Dişlerine Yönelik Tedavi Yöntemleri</span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Klinik olarak genel yaklaşımımız öncelikle ebeveynlere süt dişlerinin önemini açıklamakla birlikte süt düşlerinin mevcudiyetini korumaya yönelik gerekli bakımların yapılması hususunda onları teşvik etmektir. Fakat süt dişlerinin çürümesi ya da herhangi bir sebeple kaybedilmesi durumunda açılan diş boşluğunu diğer dişlerin diziliminin bozulmaması adına “<em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">yer tutucu”</em>&nbsp;denilen yöntemle doldurmak elzem hale gelmektedir.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Bu sayede diğer dişlerin ve gelecek olan daimi dişlerin konumu muhafaza edilir. Aksi takdirde ilerleyen zamanlarda bu gibi problemlere maruz kalmış bireylerin büyük çoğunluğunda diş teli kullanımı gerekebilmektedir. &nbsp;Bir diğer uygulama ise diş yüzeylerinde çürük ve plak oluşumunu engellemeye yönelik yapılan&nbsp;<em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">“fissur örtücü”&nbsp;</em>denilen yöntemdir.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Bu yöntem sayesinde hem süt dişleri korunur hem de daimi dişlerin sürme aşamasında meydana gelebilecek çürük oluşumlarının önüne geçilir.</p><h3 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.1; font-size: 24px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Sut_Disleri_Tedavi_Edilmeli_midir\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Sut_Disleri_Tedavi_Edilmeli_midir\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Süt Dişleri Tedavi Edilmeli midir?</span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">dSüt Dişleri Tedavi Edilmeli midir? Süt dişlenme dönemi ve karma dişlenme dönemi gelişimin en aktif olduğu döneme denk gelmektedir. Bu yüzen gelişimin bu ilk döneminde süt dişlerinin oldukça önemi büyüktür. Eğer ki çürürmüş veya başka başka bir probleme maruz kalmış süt dişleri tedavi edilmezse birçok problemle karşılaşabilmekteyiz. Örneğin bir dişin yüzeyinde oluşan çürük tedavi edilmediği sürece yanındaki dişlere yanındaki dişleri de etkileyerek o dişlerin de çürümesine neden olabilir.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Tedavi edilmediği için çekilmek zorunda kalan süt dişi ile karsı karsıya kalırsak çekimden sonra süt dişleri gerekli vazifelerini yerine getiremediği için altından gelecek dişin sürmesine rehberlik edemeyiz. Bu sebeple gelen diş çapraz bir konumda sürer ve ağızda çapraşık dişlerin oluşmasına neden olabilir. Süt dişlerinin zamanında tedavi edilmemesi çocukta ağrı veya hassasiyet gibi sorunlara neden olabilir. Bu da çocuklarda dişle ilgili konularda olumsuz fobilerin gelişmesine neden olabilir. Ağız içersinde oluşan herhangi bir çürük veya başka bir problemin agız kokusu yapması çocukta olumsuz psikolojik etkilere de neden olabilir.</p><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; line-height: 34px; font-size: 30px; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: 0px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cocuklarda_Dis_Bakimi\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Cocuklarda_Dis_Bakimi\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span>Çocuklarda Diş Bakımı<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Gelişim çağındaki çocuklar hem bilişsel yönden hem de el kabiliyeti yönünden verimli bir diş bakımı sağlayamamaktadır. Bu nedenle özellikle 5 yaşa kadar olan süreçte ebeveynlerin çocuklarının diş bakımını üstlenmeleri doğru ve sağlıklı bir yaklaşım olacaktır. &nbsp;Ek gıdaya geçiş sürecinde ağız içinde yemek artıkları oluşacağı için ağız çevresini ıslak bir tülbent yardımıyla temizlemekte fayda vardır.<img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-5691 alignright entered lazyloaded\" src=\"https://dentnis.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/cocuk-dis-tedavisi.webp\" alt=\"лечение зубов у ребенка\" width=\"560\" height=\"367\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://dentnis.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/cocuk-dis-tedavisi.webp 667w,   https://dentnis.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/cocuk-dis-tedavisi-300x197.webp 300w,   https://dentnis.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/cocuk-dis-tedavisi-223x146.webp 223w,   https://dentnis.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/cocuk-dis-tedavisi-50x33.webp 50w,   https://dentnis.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/cocuk-dis-tedavisi-114x75.webp 114w\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" data-lazy-src=\"https://dentnis.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/cocuk-dis-tedavisi.webp\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" srcset=\"https://dentnis.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/cocuk-dis-tedavisi.webp 667w,   https://dentnis.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/cocuk-dis-tedavisi-300x197.webp 300w,   https://dentnis.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/cocuk-dis-tedavisi-223x146.webp 223w,   https://dentnis.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/cocuk-dis-tedavisi-50x33.webp 50w,   https://dentnis.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/cocuk-dis-tedavisi-114x75.webp 114w\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; max-width: 100%; margin: 15px 0px 15px 15px; padding: 0px; font: inherit; float: right;\"></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Gelişimi devam eden yapılacak en büyük iyilik onlara doğru diş bakımı ve ağız hijyeni konusunda hassasiyet aşılamak, bakım alışkanlığı kazandırmak olacaktır. Bu hassasiyete sahip çocuklar diş bakımı konusunda daha özenli bireyler olacağı gibi diş tedavileri ve diş hekimi muayenesi açısından da önyargısız bireyler olarak gelişim göstereceklerdir. Çocukların 1 yaşında diş hekimi ile tanıştırılmaları yanlış uygulamalar konusunda aydınlatılmak adına faydalı olacaktır.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Bilhassa ebeveynler biberon çürüklerine karşı uyarılmalıdır. Bunu destekleyici vasfa sahip başka bir doğru yaklaşım ise çocukların 3-4 yaşında diş hekimi muayenesi ile tanışmalarıdır. 3-4 yaşlarında çocuğun tekrar muayeneye götürülmesi koruyucu önlemler açısından önemlidir. Bu süreçte ebeveynlere çocuklarının dişlerini otomatik diş fırçaları ile fırçalamaları tavsiye edilebilir. Çocuklar için üretilen diş macunu yine diş bakımı açısından önemlidir.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Ebeveynler diş hekimi tarafından doğru uygulamalarla yönlendirilmelidir. Çocuklar da ileride oluşabilecek diş tedavisi korkularına karşı önyargısız olarak büyüyecektir. Yine diş hekiminin dişlere uygulayacağı fissur örtücü tedavisi gelişim çağında yaşanabilecek diş çürüklerine karşı kalkan görevi üstlenecektir.</p><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; line-height: 34px; font-size: 30px; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: 0px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Fissur_Ortucu_Nedir\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Fissur_Ortucu_Nedir\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span>Fissür Örtücü Nedir?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Dişlerin çiğneyici yüzeylerinde olan girintili çıkıntılı yapılara fissür adı verilir. Bu yapılar yemek artıklarının en çok biriktiği ve burda kalan yemek artıklarının bakterilere beslenme kaynağı olduğu yerlerdir. Fissürleri örtmek için bu noktaların üzerine sürülen şeffaf veya beyaz akışkan maddelere fissür örtücüler denir. Fissür örtücüler akışkan olduğu için fissürlerin çukur yapısının en ince noktasına kadar girerek dişin yüzeyini çürük oluşumunu engellemek amacıyla korur. Fissür öttücü uygulaması çok basit işlemler olup tek seansta uygulanabilir. Hastanın, çocuğun hiçbir sekilde ağrı ve ya çekince duymasını gerektiren işlemler değildir. Fissür örtücüler üzerinde fissür olan bütün dişlere uygulanabilir. Yani fissürlere sahip olan büyük azı ve küçük azı dişlerine uygulanabilir. Fissür örtücü uygulamak için hiçbir yaş aralığı yoktur.&nbsp; Büyüklere de fissür örtücü uygulandığı gibi dişlerin ilk sürmeye başladığı dönemde uygulanması dişlerin çürük oluşumuna engel olması acısından oldukça önemlidir. 6 yaşında sürmeye başlayan azı dişleri fissür örtücü uygulayarak çocukların diş hekimliğiyle olumsuz bir işlem yaşamadan tedavilere başlanması çocuklarada olumlu katkı sağlayacaktır.</p><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; line-height: 34px; font-size: 30px; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: 0px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Yer_Tutucu_Nedir\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Yer_Tutucu_Nedir\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span>Yer Tutucu Nedir?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Çeşitli sebeplerle erken süt dişi kaybına uğramış durumlarda süt dişinin çekilmesi altından gelecek olan dişin yerini koruyamaması anlamına gelmektedir. Ve çekilen süt dişinin olduğu bölgeye doğru yandaki dişler devrileceği için alttan gelen dişin sürebileceği yeterli bir alan bulunmamasına neden olur. Bu yüzden erken süt dişi kaybı yaşandığı dönemlerde yandaki dişlerin oraya devrilmesini engellemek amacıyla sabit yer tutucu dediğimiz uygulamalar yapılmaktadır. Bu yer tutucu uygulamaları pasif olmakla beraber dişe hiçbir aktif kuvvet uygulamayıp sadece alttan gelecek olan dişin çene içersinde gerekli yerinin koruma amacıyla yapılmaktadır.</p><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; line-height: 34px; font-size: 30px; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: 0px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Yaslara_Gore_Cocuklarda_Dis_Bakimi_Nasil_Olmalidir\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Yaslara_Gore_Cocuklarda_Dis_Bakimi_Nasil_Olmalidir\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span>Yaşlara Göre Çocuklarda Diş Bakımı Nasıl Olmalıdır?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Çocuklarda büyüme gelişim dönemlerine göre ağız sağlığı bakımları da ceşitli farklılıklar göstermektedir. Bebek 1 yaşına gelene kadar ağız ve çevresinin ıslak bir tülbentle silinip temizlenmesi oldukça önemlidir. Bir 5 yaşındaki çocuk fonksiyonları gereğince ağız çevresinin yeterince temizleyememektedir. Bu dönemde ebeveynlerin çocukların diş fırçalamasını bizzat kendileri yapmaları gerekmektedir.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Bu dönem çocuklar için bir alışkanlık kazanma dönemi olduğu için ara ara çocuklara diş fırçalamanın nasıl olması gerektiği çocuk fırçayı eline alıp kendi dişlerini fırçaladığı sürece dönemlerde de ağız ve diş sağlığına oldukça önem gösterir. 6 yaşından sonra daimi dişler sürmeye başladığı zaman azı dişlerine fissur örtücü dediğimiz uygulamalar yapılarak çürüğe karsı önleyici bir işlem yapılmalıdır. 6-12 yaş arası yani karışık dişlenme dediğimiz dönemde süt dişleriyle daimi dişler ağız içersinde beraber bulunur. Bu dönemde süt dişlerini gerekli fizyolojik süreler boyunca ağızda tutulması gerekmektedir.</p><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; line-height: 34px; font-size: 30px; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: 0px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Biberon_Curugu_Nedir\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Biberon_Curugu_Nedir\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span>Biberon Çürüğü Nedir?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Ebeveynler, çocukların gelişim döneminde en çok çocukların beslenmesi konusunda önem vermektedir. Çocukların daha iyi beslenmesi için anne sütü veya verilen mamalara konulan sekerler ağız içersinde dişlerin yüzeyine yapışıp kalabilir. Eğer ki gece beslenme alışkanlığı olan çocuklarda daha kolay beslenmesi için biberonlara veya emziklerin ucuna bal veya reçel gibi seyler sürülebilir ebeveylerin yapmış olduğu en büyük yanlışlardan biri ise budur.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Gece boyu agız içersinde yerleşen seker dişlerin düz yüzeylerinde çürük oluşmasına neden olur. Biberon çürüğünün en belirgin özelliği dişlerin düz yüzeylerinde ortaya çıkmasıdır. Bu yüzden ebeveynlerin çocukları gece beslenme alışkanlığına alıştırmamasıdır. Daha kolay bir sekilde kabul etsin diye biberon ve emziklerin uçlarına tatlandırıcı bal şeker veya bunun gibi malzemeler sürerek çocuklarına teslim etmemesi gerekmektedir. Çocuklarını bu şekilde beslememesi gerekmektedir.</p><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; line-height: 34px; font-size: 30px; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: 0px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cocuklarin_Disleri_Neden_Curur\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Cocuklarin_Disleri_Neden_Curur\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span>Çocukların Dişleri Neden Çürür?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Süt dişlerin mine ve dentinleri daimi dişlerin neredeyse yarısı kadardır. Aynı zamanda süt dişlerin içeriğindeki organik yapı daimi dişlere göre daha fazla olduğu için çürümeye daha yatkın ve daha meyillidir. Bu dönmede ebeveynlerin çocukların ağız ve diş sağlığına gerekli önemi göstermesi ve çocuklarını bu yönde motive ve teşvik etmesi oldukça önem kazanmaktadır. Bu dönemde ebeveynlerin yapmış olduğu bir yanlış ise beslenmelerini daha önemli görmeleridir. Ayrıca gece uyurken beslenmeleri daha rahat olsun diye biberona emziğine bal reçel gibi seyler sürüp bunları ağzına takmasıdır. Bu gece tükürük akışının daha az olduğu bir dönemde şekerle buluşan mikroorganizmaların daha hızlı bir şekilde çürüğe neden olmasına sebep olacaktır.</p><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; line-height: 34px; font-size: 30px; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: 0px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Bebeklerde_Dis_Cikarmasinin_Belirtileri_Nelerdir\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Bebeklerde_Dis_Cikarmasinin_Belirtileri_Nelerdir\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span>Bebeklerde Diş Çıkarmasının Belirtileri Nelerdir?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Diş çıkarma belirtileri dişin sürmesinde 1-2 ay önce ortaya çıkabilir. Bunların en bilineni bebekte kaşıntı duygusu, bulduğu her şeyi ağzına götürerek o kaşıntı belirtisini ortadan kaldırmak istemesidir. Bunun dışında çocuklarda salya akımının artması diş sürme belirtilerinden biri olabilir. Aynı zamanda diş sürme döneminde diş etine baskı yaptığı ve diş etinde bir enflamasyon oluşturduğu için çocuklarda ağrıya neden olur. Bu ağrı sebebiyle çocuklarda oldukça huzursuz bir dönem görülebilir. çocuklar bulduğu her seyi ısırma ve kasıntısını giderme ihtiyacı duyabilir.</p><h2 class=\"title\" style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; line-height: 34px; font-size: 30px; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: 0px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cocukta_ilk_Dis_hekimi_Muayenesi_Ne_Zaman_Yapilmalidir\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Cocukta_ilk_Dis_hekimi_Muayenesi_Ne_Zaman_Yapilmalidir\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span>Çocukta ilk Diş hekimi Muayenesi Ne Zaman Yapılmalıdır?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 20px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Раньше считалось, что первый осмотр у стоматолога детям следует проходить после того, как во рту у них прорезались все зубы, то есть примерно в возрасте 2,5–3 лет.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Однако, согласно последним данным литературы, исследование показывает, что для годовалого ребенка очень важно посещать стоматолога.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Это поможет вашему годовалому ребенку привыкнуть к обстановке, в которой он впервые приходит на осмотр, и предотвратит возникновение в будущем таких явлений, как страх перед стоматологом или другие негативные мысли о стоматологе.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Любые негативные выводы или неправомерное поведение родителей в этот период предупреждаются заранее и предотвращают негативное прогрессирование состояния полости рта и зубов у детей.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Первый стоматологический осмотр у детей должен проводиться примерно в возрасте 1 года.</font></font></p><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; line-height: 34px; font-size: 30px; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: 0px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cocuk_Dis_Hekimligi_Hakkinda_Anne_Babaya_Verilecek_Ogutler_Nelerdir\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Cocuk_Dis_Hekimligi_Hakkinda_Anne_Babaya_Verilecek_Ogutler_Nelerdir\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Какой совет дать родителям по поводу детской стоматологии?</font><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Дети должны ходить к стоматологу в раннем возрасте и знакомиться со стоматологом и окружающей средой.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Стоматологов или любые процедуры, связанные со стоматологией, не следует показывать детям как пугающие.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Детей не следует запугивать этими вопросами таким образом.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Например, если вы сегодня пойдете к дантисту, вас не должны поощрять покупать игрушку, шоколад или делать все, что вы хотите.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Чтобы ребенок преодолел свой страх перед стоматологом, над ребенком не следует издеваться.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">В то же время родителям не следует выражать свои сомнения или опасения перед детьми.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Следует избегать многих видов поведения, которые могут негативно повлиять на ребенка, например этого, и у ребенка должна быть позитивная мотивация в отношении стоматологии.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Из-за таких негативных явлений, как боязнь стоматолога или боязнь стоматологического кресла, они будут постоянно избегать ухода за полостью рта и зубов, а также стоматологического лечения и будут прогрессировать в сторону более негативных последствий для здоровья.</font></font></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid\" style=\"margin: 0px -15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; width: 946.662px; position: relative; min-height: 1px; float: left;\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 15px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; width: 946.662px;\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><div class=\"wpb_video_widget wpb_content_element vc_clearfix   vc_video-aspect-ratio-169 vc_video-el-width-100 vc_video-align-left\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 35px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; width: 916.662px; float: left;\"><div class=\"wpb_video_wrapper\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 35px; padding: 515.612px 0px 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; width: 916.662px;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: start; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>', 'Детская стоматология (педодонтия) Детская стоматология (педодонтия) — общее название методов лечения зубов и полости рта, подходящих для любого этапа развития ребенка. В детской стоматологии […]', '2024-02-07 19:28:41', '2024-02-14 03:35:56');
INSERT INTO `blog_translations` (`id`, `blog_id`, `language_id`, `title`, `description`, `mini_description`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(28, 10, 2, 'Single Tooth implant', '<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Implant treatment is a very useful and precise method that can be used when multiple teeth are lost or one tooth is missing.&nbsp;</font></font></font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">In classical treatment, in case of loss of one or more teeth, the bridge method is usually preferred.&nbsp;</font></font></font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">However, over time, it was discovered that these bridge teeth are not durable and cause other problems with teeth and gums.&nbsp;</font></font></font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Cosmetic dentistry, which continues to continuously improve methods and technological advances, has now developed much stronger and more advanced treatments.</font></font></font></font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">The implantation method, which is one of these treatments, is the most preferred today due to its technical structure and durability;&nbsp;</font></font></font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">It has become the application that provides the most successful results in terms of aesthetics and health.&nbsp;</font></font></font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Therefore, bridge teeth, which have many defects, are now undoubtedly replaced by implant teeth.</font></font></font></font></p><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; line-height: 34px; font-size: 30px; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); text-align: start; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Kopru_Yontemi_ile_Tek_Dis_Implant_Yapilabilir_mi\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Kopru_Yontemi_ile_Tek_Dis_Implant_Yapilabilir_mi\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Is it possible to install a single tooth implant using a bridge method?</font><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">In cases where only one tooth is missing in the mouth, adjacent teeth must be trimmed and reduced in size to install a bridge.&nbsp;</font></font></font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Clinically, damaging healthy teeth to create a tooth is not the method we would prefer.&nbsp;</font></font></font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Moreover, the damage caused to teeth by bridge treatment is not limited to tooth reduction;&nbsp;</font></font></font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Due to the destruction of tooth enamel, the inevitable outcome is the formation of caries over time in the permanent teeth under the bridge tooth.</font></font></font></font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">In addition, bad breath may occur because bridge teeth are very suitable for the accumulation of food deposits.&nbsp;</font></font></font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Gum disease can occur in patients over time;&nbsp;</font></font></font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">if the nerves are affected&nbsp;</font></font></font></font><a data-ail=\"8031\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://dentnis.com/kanal-tedavisi/\" title=\"root canal treatment\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 122, 183); background-color: transparent; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">root canal treatment</font></a><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;may be necessary.&nbsp;</font></font></font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">In addition to fixed porcelain bridges, for which the teeth must be trimmed, there are permanent bridges that are attached to the teeth by acid etching;&nbsp;</font></font></font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">There is no need to trim teeth when using this bridge, but over time these teeth may fall out.</font></font></font></font></p><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; line-height: 34px; font-size: 30px; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); text-align: start; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tek_Dis_Implant_Avantajlari\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Tek_Dis_Implant_Avantajlari\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Benefits of single tooth implantation</font><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Based on the methods of protective and preventive medicine that we use in the clinic, we can say that implant treatment is a very tissue-friendly treatment.&nbsp;</font></font></font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Neither the teeth nor the surrounding tissues in the patient\'s mouth will be harmed, both in terms of treatment methods and materials used.&nbsp;</font></font></font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Because implant treatment is applied directly to the missing area of ​​the tooth, to the bone of the tooth, without affecting the surrounding tissues and teeth, the tooth can be placed on it independently of other teeth.&nbsp;</font></font></font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">There is no eruption, reduction or abrasion of teeth in the area where the implant is installed.</font></font></font></font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">While the tooth is placed on single-tooth implants, no intervention is made to the adjacent teeth.&nbsp;</font></font></font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">In this regard, implant treatment is a method that is safe for tissues and teeth, which solves the problem on the spot, and also corresponds to the philosophy of preventive medicine.&nbsp;</font></font></font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">At the same time, it provides an aesthetic appearance as it is compatible with natural teeth.</font></font></font></font></p>', 'Implant treatment is a very healthy and accurate method that can be applied to multiple tooth losses or to a single missing tooth. In case of loss of one or more teeth in classical treatments […]', '2024-02-07 19:30:38', '2024-02-14 03:36:49'),
(29, 10, 3, 'Имплантат одного зуба', '<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Имплантационное лечение — очень полезный и точный метод, который можно применять при потере нескольких зубов или при отсутствии одного зуба.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">При классическом лечении в случае потери одного или нескольких зубов обычно отдается предпочтение мостовидному методу.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Однако со временем выяснилось, что эти мостовидные зубы не долговечны и вызывают другие проблемы с зубами и деснами.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Эстетическая стоматология, которая продолжает непрерывно совершенствовать методы и технические достижения, на данный момент разработала гораздо более сильные и совершенные виды лечения.</font></font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Метод имплантации, являющийся одним из этих видов лечения, сегодня является наиболее предпочтительным благодаря своей технической структуре и долговечности;&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Оно стало приложением, которое обеспечивает наиболее успешные результаты с точки зрения эстетики и здоровья.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Поэтому мостовидные зубы, имеющие множество дефектов, сейчас бесспорно заменены зубами-имплантатами.</font></font></p><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; line-height: 34px; font-size: 30px; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); text-align: start; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Kopru_Yontemi_ile_Tek_Dis_Implant_Yapilabilir_mi\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Kopru_Yontemi_ile_Tek_Dis_Implant_Yapilabilir_mi\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Можно ли установить имплантат одного зуба методом моста?</font><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">В тех случаях, когда во рту отсутствует только один зуб, для установки мостовидного протеза необходимо обрезать и уменьшить в размерах соседние зубы.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Клинически, повреждение здоровых зубов для создания зуба — это не тот метод, который мы бы предпочли.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Более того, вред, причиняемый зубам мостовидным лечением, не ограничивается редукцией зубов;&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Из-за разрушения зубной эмали неизбежным исходом является образование с течением времени кариеса в постоянных зубах под мостовидным зубом.</font></font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Кроме того, может наблюдаться неприятный запах изо рта, поскольку мостовые зубы очень подходят для накопления отложений пищи.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Заболевания десен могут возникнуть у пациентов с течением времени;&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">если нервы поражены&nbsp;</font></font><a data-ail=\"8031\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://dentnis.com/kanal-tedavisi/\" title=\"лечение корневых каналов\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 122, 183); background-color: transparent; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">лечение корневых каналов</font></a><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;может быть необходимо.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Помимо несъемных фарфоровых мостовидных протезов, для которых зубы необходимо обрезать, существуют несъемные мостовидные зубы, которые прикрепляются к зубам путем травления кислотой;&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">При использовании этого моста нет необходимости обрезать зубы, но со временем эти зубы могут выпасть.</font></font></p><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; line-height: 34px; font-size: 30px; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); text-align: start; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tek_Dis_Implant_Avantajlari\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Tek_Dis_Implant_Avantajlari\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Преимущества имплантации одного зуба</font><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Основываясь на методах защитной и профилактической медицины, которые мы применяем в клинике, мы можем сказать, что лечение имплантатами является очень щадящим для тканей лечением.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Ни зубы, ни окружающие ткани во рту пациента не пострадают, как с точки зрения методов лечения, так и с точки зрения используемых материалов.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Поскольку имплантологическое лечение применяется непосредственно к отсутствующему участку зуба, к кости зуба, не затрагивая окружающие ткани и зубы, и зуб можно разместить на нем независимо от других зубов.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">В области установки имплантата не происходит прорезывания, уменьшения или истирания зубов.</font></font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-bottom: 20px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Пока зуб помещается на имплантаты, предназначенные для установки одного зуба, никакое вмешательство в соседние зубы не производится.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">В этом отношении имплантологическое лечение является безопасным для тканей и зубов методом, который решает проблему на месте, а также соответствует философии профилактической медицины.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">В то же время он обеспечивает эстетичный внешний вид, поскольку совместим с естественными зубами.</font></font></p>', 'Имплантационное лечение — очень полезный и точный метод, который можно применять при потере нескольких зубов или при отсутствии одного зуба. В случае потери одного или нескольких зубов при классическом лечении […]', '2024-02-07 19:30:38', '2024-02-14 03:36:49'),
(30, 11, 2, 'Seamless implant', '<div class=\"vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid\" style=\"margin: 0px -15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: start; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"><div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; width: 946.662px; position: relative; min-height: 1px; float: left;\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 15px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; width: 946.662px;\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><div class=\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 35px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 30px; line-height: 34px; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); letter-spacing: 0px;\">Sutureless Implant – Laser Implant<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Sutureless Implant- Laser Implant: Perhaps, for many patients, implant treatment is seen as a frightening process due to incisions and sutures made during the operation. The incision and suturing processes applied inside the mouth make individuals avoid dental operations. However, unlike conventional implant treatments, technological advances in dentistry make it possible to perform operations without incisions and suture. In this regard, Sutureless Implant- Laser Implant treatment is good news for our patients who are feared of incision and suturing. With the Sutureless Implant- Laser Implant called “Flapless surgery”, the comfort of the patients in the healing process increases after the treatment.</p><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 30px; line-height: 34px; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); letter-spacing: 0px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Sutureless_Laser_Implant_Treatment\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Sutureless_Laser_Implant_Treatment\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span>Sutureless Laser Implant Treatment<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 20px !important;\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-503 aligncenter entered lazyloaded\" src=\"https://dentnis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/dikissiz-implant-image-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"447\" height=\"298\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://dentnis.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2020/03/dikissiz-implant-image-1.jpg.webp 500w,  https://dentnis.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2020/03/dikissiz-implant-image-1-300x200.jpg.webp 300w\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 447px) 100vw, 447px\" data-lazy-src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/dikissiz-implant-image-1.jpg\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" sizes=\"(max-width: 447px) 100vw, 447px\" srcset=\"https://dentnis.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2020/03/dikissiz-implant-image-1.jpg.webp 500w,  https://dentnis.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2020/03/dikissiz-implant-image-1-300x200.jpg.webp 300w\" style=\"height: auto; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; clear: both; text-align: center; display: block;\">Sutureless Implant- Laser Implant: In the sutureless laser implant technique, there are many advantages provided by digital dentistry. Because the sutureless laser implant technique is an operation performed with completely digital dentistry. At the beginning of treatment, first of all, mouth and teeth, impressions are taken with tomography; the 3D appearance of the bone and soft tissues obtained and transferred to digital media.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Virtually the place where the implants will be located is determined within the dimensions and stents are created. Since the bone is analyzed in 3D there is no need to see it with the bare eye, implants are placed with the help of stents. The implants are placed in the patient’s mouth as planned to be placed on the computer.</p><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 30px; line-height: 34px; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); letter-spacing: 0px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Advantages_of_Sutureless_Implant\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Advantages_of_Sutureless_Implant\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span>Advantages of Sutureless Implant<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Sutureless Implant- Laser Implant: Since the incision is not made during the treatment of the sutureless laser implant, no damage given to any tissue and a more atraumatic operation process takes place. Thus, the healing process after the treatment is overcome more comfortably and quickly.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">Since the idea of suturing to any point of your body frightens many individuals, it is psychologically comforting because it is made without sutures. In the sutureless laser implant method, tissue injuries are eliminated because no cuts and sutures are made; Thus, both the risk of infection is eliminated and edema is not seen. Likewise, the patient does not feel pain during the recovery period after treatment.</p><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 30px; line-height: 34px; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); letter-spacing: 0px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cost_of_Implant_with_Sutureless_Laser\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Cost_of_Implant_with_Sutureless_Laser\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span>Cost of Implant with Sutureless Laser<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Sutureless Implant- Laser Implant: The sutureless laser implant method is a costly procedure as it is a treatment applied with special technics and equipment. However, the elements that make the implant costly with a sutureless laser also provide superiority to the sutureless implant in terms of the advantages it provides as it makes the treatment more atraumatic and the healing process more comfortable. In DentNis Cosmetic Dentistry Clinic we prefer sutureless implant application as well because of its advantages.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid\" style=\"margin: 0px -15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: start; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"><div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; width: 946.662px; position: relative; min-height: 1px; float: left;\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 15px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; width: 946.662px;\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><div class=\"wpb_video_widget wpb_content_element vc_clearfix   vc_video-aspect-ratio-169 vc_video-el-width-100 vc_video-align-left\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 35px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; width: 916.662px; float: left;\"><div class=\"wpb_video_wrapper\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 35px; padding: 515.612px 0px 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; width: 916.662px;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Dikişsiz İmplant Nedir?\" width=\"1220\" height=\"686\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/o4woQ5Tj2yo?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"\" data-rocket-lazyload=\"fitvidscompatible\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/o4woQ5Tj2yo?feature=oembed\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" class=\"entered lazyloaded\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 100%; width: 916.662px; height: 515.612px; display: block; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px;\"></iframe></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>', 'Seamless Implant What is a seamless implant? Perhaps, for many patients, implant treatment is seen as a frightening procedure due to the incisions made and stitches made during the operation. […]', '2024-02-07 19:32:46', '2024-02-14 03:37:41');
INSERT INTO `blog_translations` (`id`, `blog_id`, `language_id`, `title`, `description`, `mini_description`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(31, 11, 3, 'Бесшовный имплантат', '<div class=\"vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid\" style=\"margin: 0px -15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: start; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"><div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; width: 946.662px; position: relative; min-height: 1px; float: left;\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 15px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; width: 946.662px;\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><div class=\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 35px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; line-height: 34px; font-size: 30px; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: 0px;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Бесшовный имплантат – лазерный имплантат</font><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 20px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Бесшовная имплантация – лазерная имплантация. Возможно, для многих пациентов установка имплантатов воспринимается как пугающий процесс из-за разрезов и наложения швов, сделанных во время операции.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Процессы разреза и наложения швов, применяемые внутри рта, заставляют людей избегать стоматологических операций.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Однако, в отличие от традиционного лечения имплантатами, технологические достижения в стоматологии позволяют выполнять операции без разрезов и наложения швов.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">В этом отношении лечение лазерной имплантацией без швов является хорошей новостью для наших пациентов, которые боятся разреза и наложения швов.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Благодаря бесшовному лазерному имплантату под названием «Безлоскутная хирургия» после лечения повышается комфорт пациентов в процессе заживления.</font></font></p><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; line-height: 34px; font-size: 30px; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: 0px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Sutureless_Laser_Implant_Treatment\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Sutureless_Laser_Implant_Treatment\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Бесшовное лазерное лечение имплантатов</font><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 20px !important;\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-503 aligncenter entered lazyloaded\" src=\"https://dentnis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/dikissiz-implant-image-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"447\" height=\"298\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://dentnis.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2020/03/dikissiz-implant-image-1.jpg.webp 500w,  https://dentnis.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2020/03/dikissiz-implant-image-1-300x200.jpg.webp 300w\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 447px) 100vw, 447px\" data-lazy-src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/dikissiz-implant-image-1.jpg\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" sizes=\"(max-width: 447px) 100vw, 447px\" srcset=\"https://dentnis.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2020/03/dikissiz-implant-image-1.jpg.webp 500w,  https://dentnis.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2020/03/dikissiz-implant-image-1-300x200.jpg.webp 300w\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font: inherit; clear: both; text-align: center; display: block;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Бесшовная имплантация – лазерная имплантация: технология бесшовной лазерной имплантации имеет множество преимуществ, предоставляемых цифровой стоматологией.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Потому что техника бесшовной лазерной имплантации — это операция, выполняемая с помощью полностью цифровой стоматологии.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">В начале лечения в первую очередь снимают слепки полости рта и зубов с помощью томографии;&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">3D-вид костей и мягких тканей, полученный и перенесенный на цифровой носитель.</font></font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 20px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Практически в пределах размеров определяется место, где будут располагаться имплантаты, и создаются стенты.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Поскольку кость анализируется в 3D, нет необходимости видеть ее невооруженным глазом, имплантаты устанавливаются с помощью стентов.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Имплантаты помещаются в рот пациента, как и планировалось на компьютере.</font></font></p><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; line-height: 34px; font-size: 30px; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: 0px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Advantages_of_Sutureless_Implant\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Advantages_of_Sutureless_Implant\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Преимущества бесшовного имплантата</font><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 20px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Бесшовный имплантат - лазерный имплантат: поскольку во время лечения бесшовным лазерным имплантатом разрез не делается, никакие ткани не повреждаются, а процесс операции происходит более атравматично.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Таким образом, процесс выздоровления после лечения проходит более комфортно и быстро.</font></font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 20px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Поскольку идея наложения швов на любую точку тела пугает многих людей, она психологически утешительна, поскольку делается без швов.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">При бесшовном методе лазерной имплантации исключается травмирование тканей, поскольку не накладываются разрезы и швы;&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Таким образом, исключается риск заражения и не наблюдается отеков.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Также пациент не чувствует боли в период восстановления после лечения.</font></font></p><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; line-height: 34px; font-size: 30px; color: rgb(209, 72, 145); padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: 0px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cost_of_Implant_with_Sutureless_Laser\" ez-toc-data-id=\"#Cost_of_Implant_with_Sutureless_Laser\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Стоимость имплантата с использованием бесшовного лазера</font><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Бесшовная имплантация - лазерная имплантация. Метод бесшовной лазерной имплантации является дорогостоящей процедурой, поскольку это лечение, применяемое с использованием специальной техники и оборудования.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Однако элементы, которые делают установку имплантата с помощью бесшовного лазера дорогостоящим, также обеспечивают превосходство над бесшовным имплантатом с точки зрения предоставляемых им преимуществ, поскольку он делает лечение более атравматичным, а процесс заживления более комфортным.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">В клинике косметической стоматологии DentNis мы отдаем предпочтение бесшовной установке имплантатов еще и из-за ее преимуществ.</font></font></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid\" style=\"margin: 0px -15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: start; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"><div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; width: 946.662px; position: relative; min-height: 1px; float: left;\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 15px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; width: 946.662px;\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><div class=\"wpb_video_widget wpb_content_element vc_clearfix   vc_video-aspect-ratio-169 vc_video-el-width-100 vc_video-align-left\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 35px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; width: 916.662px; float: left;\"><div class=\"wpb_video_wrapper\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 35px; padding: 515.612px 0px 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; width: 916.662px;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Что такое бесшовный имплантат?\" width=\"1220\" height=\"686\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/o4woQ5Tj2yo?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"\" data-rocket-lazyload=\"fitvidscompatible\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/o4woQ5Tj2yo?feature=oembed\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" class=\"entered lazyloaded\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 100%; width: 916.662px; height: 515.612px; display: block; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px;\"></iframe></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>', 'Бесшовный имплантат Что такое бесшовный имплантат? Пожалуй, для многих пациентов имплантологическое лечение воспринимается как пугающая процедура из-за сделанных во время операции разрезов и швов. […]', '2024-02-07 19:32:46', '2024-02-14 03:37:41'),
