; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); background-color: transparent;\">Carl E. Misch</a></span>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.goldsteingarber.com/about-us/for-doctors\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); background-color: transparent;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Maurice Salama</span></a>,&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dennis_P._Tarnow\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); background-color: transparent;\">Dennis P. Tarnow</a></span>,&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><a href=\"https://www.ideausa.net/faculty/fouad-khoury/\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); background-color: transparent;\">Prof. Dr. Fouad Khoury</a></span>&nbsp;gibi araştırmacılardan&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><a data-ail=\"4168\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://dentnis.com/bir-gunde-implant/\" title=\"bir günde implant\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); background-color: transparent;\">bir günde implant</a>&nbsp;</span>ve yönlendirilmiş doku rejenarasyonu eğitimleri alarak klinisyenliğe ağırlık vermiştir. Özellikle estetik ve&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><a data-mil=\"4168\" href=\"https://dentnis.com/kozmetik-dis-hekimligi-nedir-tedavileri-nelerdir/\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); background-color: transparent;\">kozmetik diş hekimliğinde</a></span>&nbsp;implant cerrahisi ile&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><a data-ail=\"4168\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://dentnis.com/gulus-tasarimi/\" title=\"gülüş tasarımı\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); background-color: transparent;\">gülüş tasarımı</a>&nbsp;</span>konularına eğilerek, ön bölge restorasyonlarda&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><a data-mil=\"4168\" href=\"https://dentnis.com/pembe-estetik/\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); background-color: transparent;\">pembe estetik</a>&nbsp;</span>ve diş eti papil oluşumu üzerine klinik calışmalar yapmıştır.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 20px !important;\">2011 yılında ekibi ile birlikte&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><a data-mil=\"4168\" href=\"https://dentnis.com/hakkimizda/\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); background-color: transparent;\">Nisantaşı DentNis Estetik Diş ve İmplantoloji Diş Kliniği’ni</a></span>&nbsp;kurmuştur.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-famil